"  The pulled pork:","4 1/2 pounds pork butt on the bone","1  (14.5 oz.) can chicken broth","1 tablespoon distilled vinegar","1 cup barbecue sauce","  The coleslaw:","1  (1 lb.) bag shredded cabbage","1/2 cup plain low-fat yogurt","1/2 cup light mayonnaise","1 tablespoon distilled white vinegar","1 teaspoon sugar"